			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. Talk to Hope in House of Hope and promise to help&#xD;&#xA;teleport S_LOW_HouseOfHope_HopeIntroduction_Trigger&#xD;&#xA;3. Talk to Eternal Debtor&#xD;&#xA;teleport S_LOW_HouseOfHope_MerregonDebtor04" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="23" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="A dialogue with one of the &quot;guards&quot; in House of Hope. &#xD;&#xA;These are Eternal Debters, each one has a story how did they manage to get into Raphael's hands (but not everyone will share it, to keep this in mind for writing all Merregon Debtor characters)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;These characters see players as &quot;guests&quot; of House of Hope and they don't know anything about players. " />
